~Version
VERS. 2.0 : CWLS LAS version
WRAP. NO  : One line per depth step
~Well
STRT.M 1000.0 : Start depth
STOP.M 1002.0 : Stop depth
STEP.M 1.0    : Step
NULL. -999.25 : Null value
WELL. DEMO-1  : Well name
~Curve
DEPT.M  : Measured depth
C1.PPM  : Methane
C2.PPM  : Ethane
C3.PPM  : Propane
IC4.PPM : Iso-butane
NC4.PPM : Normal butane
IC5.PPM : Iso-pentane
NC5.PPM : Normal pentane
~ASCII
